ZH: 我的银行余额不足以支付这个账单。
EN: My bank balance is not sufficient to pay this bill.

ZH: 请问你银行账户里还有余额吗？
EN: May I ask if there is any balance left in your bank account?

ZH: 遗憾的是，您的账户余额已经不足以完成这笔交易。
EN: Unfortunately, your account balance is insufficient to complete this transaction.

ZH: 我的手机余额已经快用完了，得及时充值。
EN: My mobile phone balance is running low, I need to recharge it soon.

ZH: 你可以通过查询账户余额来查看阁下的积分余额。
EN: You can check your points balance by querying your account balance.

ZH: 我忘记了我的会员卡的余额密码。
EN: I forgot the balance password of my membership card.

ZH: 请通过查询账户余额来确认你的消费金额。
EN: Please confirm your purchase amount by checking your account balance.

ZH: 这张礼品卡还有多少余额？
EN: How much balance is left on this gift card?

ZH: 请及时存入足够的余额以避免透支费用。
EN: Please deposit enough balance on time to avoid overdraft fees.

ZH: 他提前偿还了房屋贷款的余额。
EN: He paid off the remaining balance of the mortgage in advance.

ZH: 余额不足以支付的部分将会从押金中扣除。
EN: The amount not covered by the balance will be deducted from the deposit.

ZH: 我的信用卡额度与余额之和不能超过限制。
EN: The sum of my credit card limit and balance cannot exceed the limit.

ZH: 请问您的会员卡还有多少余额？
EN: May I ask how much balance is left on your membership card?

ZH: 请确认您支付的金额和账户余额是否一致。
EN: Please confirm if the amount you paid matches your account balance.

ZH: 他在银行里存了一大笔余额。
EN: He has a large balance deposited in the bank.

ZH: 请确保您的账户余额足够支付这笔交易。
EN: Please make sure your account balance is sufficient to pay for this transaction.

ZH: 请提供您的账户余额证明。
EN: Please provide proof of your account balance.

ZH: 我想了解一下我的交通卡的余额。
EN: I would like to check the balance of my transportation card.

ZH: 我们将在您的账户余额不足时发送提醒短信。
